149
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:08,040
Want to join?

150
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,330
That's too much.

151
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:50,750
What are you looking at?

152
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:52,300
Nothing.

153
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,330
I was admiring

154
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,600
