166
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,580
Hotpot's the best.

167
00:08:24,850 --> 00:08:26,020
It's so yummy.

168
00:08:26,650 --> 00:08:27,870
It's because this pot is good.

169
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:28,750
Right, honey?

170
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:36,460
