295
00:13:59,790 --> 00:14:00,830
But actually...

296
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:04,070
I've made progress.

297
00:14:04,710 --> 00:14:06,430
Lately, I've been

298
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:07,970
